"#feedbackModal_main_2531212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qdq1665702742736.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdq1665702742736.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdq1665702742736.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qdq1665702742736\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Customize WRD Error Messages\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Uniface provides a set of WRD error messages, which you can customize to your liking.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__topic_d23060e1_d23061e1_d23062e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__p_d23063e1_d23064e1_d23065e1\">To modify the WRD error messages:</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11306e1_d11307e1_d11308e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__p_d23066e1_d23067e1_d23068e1\">Locate the appropriate HTML file:\n <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WebAppDirectory</var>/error_<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>/err<var class=\"keyword varname\">GSS</var>.htm</span>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11309e1_d11310e1_d11311e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WebAppDirectory</var>—physical directory corresponding to the Web application’s virtual directory, for example <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceAPSInstallDir</var>/uniface/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11312e1_d11313e1_d11314e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>—two-letter code specifying the national language of your errors, for example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">en</code> for English, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">nl</code> for Dutch.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11315e1_d11316e1_d11317e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">G</var>—one-digit number indicating the group number of the error. Allowed values are:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11318e1_d11319e1_d11320e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> (General)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11321e1_d11322e1_d11323e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> (Server Extension)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11324e1_d11325e1_d11326e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code> (Core)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11327e1_d11328e1_d11329e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">3</code> (Middleware)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11330e1_d11331e1_d11332e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">4</code> (Request)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11333e1_d11334e1_d11335e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SS</var>—sequential two-digit number, starting at <code class=\"ph codeph\">00</code>. This, along with the group number, indicates the actual error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__p_d23069e1_d23070e1_d23071e1\">In the default Tomcat configuration, you can find English error files under the directory:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__p_d23072e1_d23073e1_d23074e1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceAPSInstallDir</var>/uniface/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF/error_en</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qdq1665702742736__li_d11336e1_d11337e1_d11338e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Modify the error text as required, in keeping with the rest of your web site.\n </span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531212\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Customize WRD Error Messages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Customize WRD Error Messages Uniface provides a set of WRD error messages, which you can customize to your liking. To modify the WRD error messages: Locate the appropriate HTML file: WebAppDirectory /error_ Language /err GSS .htm WebAppDirectory —physical directory corresponding to the Web application’s virtual directory, for example UnifaceAPSInstallDir /uniface/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF Language —two-letter code specifying the national language of your errors, for example, en for English, and nl for Dutch. G —one-digit number indicating the group number of the error. Allowed values are: 0 (General) 1 (Server Extension) 2 (Core) 3 (Middleware) 4 (Request) SS —sequential two-digit number, starting at 00 . This, along with the group number, indicates the actual error. In the default Tomcat configuration, you can find English error files under the directory: UnifaceAPSInstallDir /uniface/webapps/uniface/WEB-INF/error_en Modify the error text as required, in keeping with the rest of your web site. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}